Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, we're going to raise Kaleido Star's curtain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nyou should keep your room brightly lit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally realized what\NI forgot to take care of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason my heart is\Npounding and I can't slow it down...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now I'm not her senior in\Nthe troupe, nor am I her partner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I stand before her as a rival. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've come back. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give me your best shot, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla Hamilton, the Golden Phoenix.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa aka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:09.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:24.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:10.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:17.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contest is on, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, step down from your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd practice more up until opening\Nday and aim to be a true Kaleido Star, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can become one\Nof those just by practicing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I entrusted that dream to you because\NI thought you had something that I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still hadn't figured that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've mastered the Angel's Maneuver too,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to do battle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you'll consider me a worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still decline the challenge,\Nyou're nothing but a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any intent of\Nbecoming a true Kaleido Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then surpass me, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Battle Miss Layla for a role? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My blood is starting to race\Njust thinking about it. Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hold back the desire to challenge her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you're up for the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Most Amazing and Inescapable Showdown."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three. One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you find this strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:04:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three. One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's talking about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they don't care\Nwhich one gets the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they really want both of them to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nobody's got any choice but to\Ndo what they need to be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who ends up being the lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that you've decided to do this,\Ngive your own role all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it'll be hard to do with\Nthe time and budget we have, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}it{\i0}! It definitely has to be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The decision is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to do it, I'll start work right away,\Neven if it's just tearing down the current set.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to do it, make it brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make my debut as a clown,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely {\i1}must {\i0}master this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About a thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really staking\Neverything on this show, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die, Miss Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'll get the hang of it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can stop here.\NNow get plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd refuse her,\Nsaying you didn't want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am contradictory, aren't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't hold back my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is the one who taught me\Nboth the fun and the harshness of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always far ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she became a goal for me to strive for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now she's come\Nback to the stage as my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Miss Layla, who left the Kaleido\NStage because of a shoulder injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it must have been so painful\Nto master the Angel's Maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I want to go up\Nagainst her with all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is special to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to meet Layla was your\Ngreatest stroke of fortune, wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Sophie nor I had such good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was the one who tied Sophie down\Nand let all her possibilities go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to atone for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to go out onto the stage\Nand I destroyed partner after partner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to find a true star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've committed so many wrongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a true star is realized,\NI may at least be allowed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo turns its fangs on Sagittarius,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its brightness increased to\Nalmost ferocious brilliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come all the way here\Nbecause you were worried about Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both constellations shine intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their fate is that if they collide,\None of them must disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a constellation\Nthat had already disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the moment\NI realized I could still see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pondered what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did think that the role left to\Nme might be to guide Sora on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet in the end my actions\Nonly caused Sora to take a detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But watching Sora regain\Nher brilliance, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't been allowed\Nto step down from this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just return once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like May, who made her comeback\Neven after Leon wrecked her shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:07:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this demon may end\Nup destroying the true Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find that out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't been this excited in a long time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm on fire. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's strange... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's still a battle, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but there's none of that\Npain there was at the Festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the opposite. I'm happy that I can fight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass me, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With all I've got, so there's no regrets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Mr. Leon is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have an important audition today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care not to get in the way of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but Chinese for breakfast is so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, power up, go at\Nher head-on and be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be crushed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you losing too pathetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just seeing Miss Layla's Angel's Maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your Angel's Maneuver too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry up and eat already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, eat this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver is\Nsaid to require innate instinct;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you mastered\Nit to this degree of perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I couldn't do that, this\Ncontest would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt this feeling before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was the first time\NI stood on the Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it was my first\Naudition for a lead role...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the first time you\Npulled off the Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like those feelings\Nwere all different than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my heart is dancing so much at\Nthe thought of today's performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not long now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the "true Kaleido Star"\Nyou dreamed of will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is thrilling. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look like Sora will fulfill our dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have high hopes for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll set very high hopes for her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a door that only those\Nwho have kept on dreaming can open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scene 32. The angel's flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Miss Sophie was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You treasured her above everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Miss Sophie must\Nhave felt that way about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think maybe having someone you\Ncan feel that way about is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were Miss Sophie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I would want\Nyou to suffer trying to atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the stage is nothing\Nbut pain for you, Mr. Leon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you shouldn't go out onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this audition myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going onstage,\Ndo it for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my own sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out there together\Nand get the best kind of applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a real Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best kind of applause, with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I keep going straight down,\NI think I'll hit trapeze A-2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can tell. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I keep going straight\Ndown, I'll hit trapeze A-5.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're both perfect. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a technical level they're equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sora's Odette is lively and vigorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla kind of projects an air of innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Layla for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think after all this time, she's\Nstill showing us a new side of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell how this battle will play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both great, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge amount of tension in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'll start\Nhaving trouble breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good for you, Sora, coming this far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now clear your own path on your own power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the first rival I've been able\Nto compete with on an equal level.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can feel your burning\Nenthusiasm all through my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back then, I never dreamed\Na day like this would come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first time I saw you perform,\NI was actually angry, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, the audience\Nwill come here just to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kalos, it's just like you foresaw.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, actually, she probably overcame each\Nordeal with more strength than you'd imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then she became my partner, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and now she's here as my rival. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to win against you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Miss Layla's onstage, the air crackles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her true drive to utterly defeat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}makes me even more fired up. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I lose my focus even a tiny bit, I'll lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Angel's Maneuver\Nawakens everyone's angel hearts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to perform my Angel's Maneuver!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, I know, why don't\NI try performing more freely?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put a little ad-lib in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's performance has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Angel's Maneuver is sure to\Nawaken everyone's angel hearts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My angel heart... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The people who gave me an angel heart,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my four parents... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Yume. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone must have people\Nwho are important to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe our angel hearts are treasures\Ngiven to us by the people important to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is adding ad-lib to her performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla is seriously trying to beat Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be doing the Angel's Maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that relentlessness is like a demon's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon that raises an angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Layla all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The you who wants Sora to surpass you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the you who wants to win against Sora...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which one of them is the real you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or are they both the real you? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a tranquil performance... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hardly believe you're vying for a role.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This feeling is... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the stage and the\Naudience are wreathed in smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be on that\Nkind of stage too, right Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why it is... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The atmosphere is the audience\Nis quickly becoming tranquil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world has happened? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, isn't there something\Nstrange about Layla's angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I used to write all kinds of\Nstories for my grandma and tell them to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered how she used to smile\Nthose times, like she was having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was remembering\Nthe first picture book I ever wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was crap, but I remember\NI gave it to a sick friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered my first diabolo show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone in the first row of the audience\Nclapped for me and shouted "Amazing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered telling gags for my mother\Nwhen she cried, trying to make her laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't think they were funny,\Nbut I got her to smile again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I asked my\Nmom to teach me the trampoline,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she looked happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I remembering this? It's got\Nnothing to do with skating or Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember teaching my little\Nbrothers pro wrestling moves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May Wong Devil Headhang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I started skating lessons,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I didn't play with them much anymore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This room is so warm. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fervor of the audience\Nhas completely vanished.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it because of Sora? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've felt this feeling before. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was then. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The day I made my busy mother\Nand father rearrange their schedules,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when I came to the\NKaleido Stage for the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was excited about what was about to happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the feeling of an audience member.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the way here I was already\Nlooking forward to Sora's performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to see Sora's angel. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this battle\Nhas been settled, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mr. Kenneth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say a true prima turns\Neven her co-stars into spectators.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was competing with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I knew it I found myself your audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hold back my desire\Nto see your Angel's Maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally surpassed me, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you just arrived at the\Ngates of true Kaleido Stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, many novices will come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drawn by their admiration of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, what you have\Nto do is take your challengers head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a wall for them to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must fight with all\Nyour strength and be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what I came to do today,\Nwhat I forgot to do before I left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up leaving the stage\Nwithout being defeated by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hindered your independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving your challengers a battle will be\Nanother important duty of yours from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The results of the audition have been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the days left until opening day,\Nall of you give everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
