Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.40,0:23:38.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone. Surechigau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:39.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
