Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:23:57.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Kaleido Star: New Wings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your wish comes true\Nsomeday, you're not alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really cried a lot. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really laughed a lot. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was really frustrated. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was really happy. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're really feeling lots of gratitude\Nas we send you the next episode,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a success story of those in the bloom of youth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.06,0:24:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The final episode of Kaleido Star:\N"To the Amazing Promised Place."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone together now! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And on towards the sky! {\i0}
